线索二叉树是一种特殊的二叉树，它将节点的左右指针用于存储前驱和后继节点，从而实现遍历的高效性。下面是一种基于中序遍历的线索二叉树的实现方式：

```java
class ThreadedBinaryTreeNode {
    int data;
    ThreadedBinaryTreeNode left, right;
    boolean isLeftThreaded, isRightThreaded;
}

class ThreadedBinaryTree {
    ThreadedBinaryTreeNode root;

    // 中序遍历线索化二叉树
    public void inorderThread() {
        ThreadedBinaryTreeNode current = root;
        ThreadedBinaryTreeNode prev = null;

        while (current != null) {
            // 找到最左边的节点
            while (current.left != null && !current.isLeftThreaded) {
                current = current.left;
            }

            // 记录当前节点的前驱节点
            if (prev != null) {
                prev.right = current;
                prev.isRightThreaded = true;
            }

            // 找到当前节点的后继节点
            ThreadedBinaryTreeNode next = current.right;
            while (next != null && next.isLeftThreaded) {
                next = next.left;
            }

            // 更新当前节点和前驱节点
            prev = current;
            current = next;
        }
    }

    // 中序遍历线索二叉树
    public void inorderTraversal() {
        ThreadedBinaryTreeNode current = root;

        while (current != null) {
            // 找到最左边的节点
            while (current.left != null && !current.isLeftThreaded) {
                current = current.left;
            }

            // 访问当前节点
            System.out.print(current.data + " ");

            // 找到当前节点的后继节点
            if (current.isRightThreaded) {
                current = current.right;
            } else {
                current = current.right;
                while (current != null && !current.isLeftThreaded) {
                    current = current.left;
                }
            }
        }
    }
}
```

在上述代码中，`ThreadedBinaryTreeNode`表示线索二叉树的节点，包含节点的值、左右子节点、是否左右线索化的标记等信息。`ThreadedBinaryTree`表示线索二叉树，包含根节点和线索化等操作。`inorderThread`方法用于对线索二叉树进行中序遍历线索化，`inorderTraversal`方法用于对线索二叉树进行中序遍历。

在响应式网站设计中，自适应字体大小是通过 CSS 的 viewport 单位（vw 和 vh）和媒体查询实现的。Viewport 单位是相对于浏览器视口的单位，1vw 等于视口宽度的 1%，1vh 等于视口高度的 1%。因此，使用 viewport 单位可以根据不同的视口大小自动调整字体大小。

以下是一个示例 CSS 代码，它使用 viewport 单位和媒体查询来实现自适应字体大小：

```css
h1 {
  font-size: 6vw; /* 字体大小为视口宽度的 6% */
}

@media screen and (min-width: 768px) {
  h1 {
    font-size: 3em; /* 当视口宽度大于 768px 时，字体大小为 3em */
  }
}
```

在这个示例中，h1 元素的字体大小设置为视口宽度的 6%，这意味着在不同的设备上，字体大小会根据视口大小而自动调整。在媒体查询中，当视口宽度大于或等于 768px 时，字体大小设置为 3em，这是为了确保在大屏幕设备上字体大小不会太小。

通过这种方式，您可以根据不同的设备和屏幕大小自动调整字体大小，从而提高网站的可读性和用户体验。

Google Apps Script is a powerful tool that allows you to automate tasks within various Google services, such as Google Sheets, Google Docs, and Google Drive. Here's an example of how you can use Google Apps Script to automate a task:

Let's say you have a Google Sheet with a list of email addresses, and you want to send each person on the list a personalized email. Here are the steps you can follow to automate this task using Google Apps Script:

1. Open the Google Sheet with the list of email addresses.

2. Click on "Tools" and select "Script editor".

3. In the script editor, write a script that retrieves the email addresses from the sheet and sends a personalized email to each address.

Here's an example script:

```
function sendEmails() {
  var sheet = SpreadsheetApp.getActiveSheet();
  var startRow = 2; // Start at row 2, since row 1 contains headers
  var numRows = sheet.getLastRow() - 1; // Get the number of rows with data
  var dataRange = sheet.getRange(startRow, 1, numRows, 2); // Get the email addresses and names
  var data = dataRange.getValues(); // Convert the data to an array

  for (var i = 0; i < data.length; i++) {
    var emailAddress = data[i][0];
    var name = data[i][1];
    var subject = "Personalized Email";
    var message = "Dear " + name + ",\n\nThis is a personalized email sent using Google Apps Script.";
    MailApp.sendEmail(emailAddress, subject, message);
  }
}
```

4. Save the script and run it by clicking on the "Run" button or by selecting "sendEmails" from the "Select function" dropdown and clicking on the "Run" button.

Once you've set up this script, it will automatically send a personalized email to each email address on the list. This can save you a lot of time and effort, especially if you have a large list of email addresses to send emails to.
